text:
If you want to experience calmness of mountains, ever flowing freshness of rivers, sweet chirping of birds, fragrance of flowers, freeness of blue skys and peace of deep forests, you listen to Mohit Chauhan. 
Mohit is Music, Mohit is Magic, Incredible Human Being, Mesmerizing Singer, Superstar Performer. 
Mohit, please tell, whether to watch your Amazing Performance, or close our eyes and listen to your Heavenly Voice.
What a Manly Matured and still Soothing Innocent Voice you have.
Not easy at all to play mouth organ, guitar at same time and sing along. You do it so fluently.
You have given global recognition to pahadi folk music.
YOU DESERVE GRAMMY

text: Absolutely haunting ending, a pretty pretty great movie. Definite must watch. Everyone’s praising DP, but Ananya was so natural and superb too, really portrayed her character well. The music kinda sealed the deal in the end.
